1. Create reusable multi-threaded queue implementation
   and rewrite the messaging system to use it (currently
   it uses pipes) and also rewrite the player to use it
   (currently using an inlined implementation).

2. Integrate curl into download manager to allow
   downloading of http, ftp, etc.

3. Write plugin system for writing search plugins
   using javascript through spidermonkey.

4. Fix player bug (the scaling filter crashes with
   some aspect ratios/screen resolution combo)

5. Fix rewind/fast foward.

6. Finish libdrm dumb buffers driver.

7. Fix problems with audio driver (it doesn't work with
   pulseaudio and audio may get choppy after a while until
   paused on some audio hardware).
